## Proposed Changes

### 1. Base de données — Nouvelle table `spin_history`

#### [NEW] Migration SQL

```sql
CREATE TABLE `spin_history` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `user_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `prize_number` int(11) NOT NULL COMMENT 'Numéro du segment (1-10)',
  `prize_label` varchar(100) NOT NULL COMMENT 'Ex: 🏷️ -10% Solde',
  `is_win` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT 0,
  `created_at` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT current_timestamp(),
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `idx_user_id` (`user_id`),
  KEY `idx_created_at` (`created_at`),
  CONSTRAINT `fk_spin_user` FOREIGN KEY (`user_id`) 
    REFERENCES `users` (`id`) ON DELETE CASCADE
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_general_ci;
```

| Colonne | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| `user_id` | FK vers `users.id` |
| `prize_number` | Segment gagné (1-10) |
| `prize_label` | Texte du prix affiché |
| `is_win` | `1` = gain, `0` = "Rien" |
| `created_at` | Horodatage du spin |

