## Architecture du Flux

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant U as Utilisateur
    participant JS as spin.js (Frontend)
    participant PHP as index.php → SpinController
    participant DB as MySQL (spin_history)

    U->>JS: Tire le levier
    JS->>JS: Calcule le segment gagnant
    JS->>U: Affiche l'overlay du prix
    JS->>PHP: POST /index.php?action=saveSpin
    PHP->>DB: INSERT INTO spin_history
    DB-->>PHP: OK
    PHP-->>JS: {success: true}
    
    U->>JS: Clique "📜 Historique"
    JS->>PHP: GET /index.php?action=getSpinHistory
    PHP->>DB: SELECT * FROM spin_history WHERE user_id=?
    DB-->>PHP: Résultats
    PHP-->>JS: JSON [{prize_label, is_win, created_at}, ...]
    JS->>U: Affiche le panneau d'historique
```

